Boil water and butter one minute.  Slowly stir in flour.  Boil another minute.  Cool.  Add eggs, one at a time.  Roll thin on flowered board and form figure eights.  Arrange figures on batter sheet and fill with filling mix.  Bake in oven at 300 for 20 to 30 minutes.
